data.description:
Get ready for some serious space and a primo location with this newly renovated 6 bedroom, 4 bathroom haven in Kyle, Texas! Tucked away on a corner lot, it's just a hop, skip, and a jump to I-35 to reach both Austin or San Antonio. Perfect for families and professionals who want to live near the heart of it all. The main floor's primary bedroom is a breeze to access, perfect if stairs aren't your thing. Meanwhile, the 5 bedrooms upstairs give everyone plenty of room to stretch out. Plus, the kitchen will make you feel like a pro chef with its sleek appliances, epic counter space, and plenty of storage.
Head outside to the sprawling backyard and covered front porch, where you can soak up that Texas sun and enjoy the breeze. And, let's not forget, this gem is smack-dab in a growing area, making it a wise investment for years to come! Don't wait to check out this beauty, it's just waiting for you to make it your dream home. Schedule a viewing today and get ready to fall in love!
